item.description:
Exeter might be an excellent location for an additional SeaL MeetUp.

Its easy enough for me to hang around after work and go to The Coat, but I know there are liberty folk southwest of Portsmouth who may otherwise be inclined to attend if a MeetUp were held closer to home.

If successful, seacoast residents interested in attending a SeaL MeetUp would be no more than a 20 minute drive to either of the host towns (Dover, Portsmouth or Exeter?)

We'll be meeting at the bar at restaurant 11 Water Street. The bar *does* serve food, you can check out the lunch (bar) menu here (http://11waterstreet....)

Depending on turnout/demand, I would hope that this may turn into an ongoing event. Hope to see you there!
item.name: The First Exeter Liberty MeetUp!
